dct_title_s: Brisbane & Queensland : scale 1:10,000 - 3,6000,000/ International Travel Maps ; cartography by Andrew Alfred-Duggan
dct_description_sm: Relief on map of Queensland shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Depths on same map shown by bathymetric tints. Panel title. Copyright: ITMB Publishing Ltd. Includes indexes, inset of Brisbane region, inset and ancillary maps showing local transit in Brisbane, ancillary tourist map of Sydney, and color illustrations
